release_body:
Release with version 2.1.0.
Changes since last release with version 2.0.5 include:
- New __PrepExternalSchema__ process implementation;
- New argument options in the __AlleleCall__ process (--CDS, --st) and a timestamp is added to new alleles names;
- New argument option in the __CreateSchema__ process (--CDS);
- __ExtractCgMLST__ process optimization;
- Prodigal training files included in the package;
- Bug correction;
